{"tid":871390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯剋星】張學友演唱會再有逃犯落網　4月以來超過30名逃犯被捕","createTime":"2018-10-22T01:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T02:51:47.000Z","uid":55851,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f584ecf249019c2d63a49e81d24c65d5b31998d9","tid":871390,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1918424/org/ebdae021f4fa2a1f32ad9736388bb316.jpg/MoaiYkYU2JVuRJJ2tPvB_Eu58w_avkqb7L8gCOy_IAg?v=w1760r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1918424%2Forg%2Febdae021f4fa2a1f32ad9736388bb316.jpg%2FMoaiYkYU2JVuRJJ2tPvB_Eu58w_avkqb7L8gCOy_IAg%3Fv%3Dw1760r16_9&h=c4c4ce55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20181022_20181022-085500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20181022_20181022-085500.jpg&h=95c99992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安徽合肥市警方在香港歌手張學友舉行演唱會期間，透過人臉識別系統成功緝拿最少九名逃犯歸案。警方在微博公布，演唱會結束後，經點算共有九名網上逃犯被捕，他們承認並非為看演唱會而到合肥。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，自從張學友今年四月在全國多處舉行演唱會以來，已經有超過三十名逃犯被警方拘捕，張學友因而有逃犯剋星的稱號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1036682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1036682&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=fd86fbfa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1036682</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">【罪犯剋星】張學友陝西演唱會18人被捕　警事前發帖：已經準備好<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/L3DvBL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FL3DvBL&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f1af74b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/L3DvBL</a><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯剋星】張學友再「發功」　在石家莊開個唱三名逃犯落網<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/gTTT82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FgTTT82&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3a0ff75f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/gTTT82</a><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯剋星】張學友演唱會現場再有逃犯落網　3個月內已4人被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/29NH9p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F29NH9p&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c4f50489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/29NH9p</a></span>"},{"pid":"d82eb3a11febd2b03f9af641baa09cc0712795ab","tid":871390,"uid":103230,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:44:57.000Z","msg":"我愛黎明"},{"pid":"5dd4c4af3ebb72c6d640f33cfdf8649e78daabf7","tid":871390,"uid":113000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"安哂閉路做人面識別就真<br />\n可以估計到監控已經去到好深入既地步"},{"pid":"f8596eec4ccca3b77ea15c7e847ea5e986ee649c","tid":871390,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5dd4c4af3ebb72c6d640f33cfdf8649e78daabf7","tid":871390,"uid":113000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"安哂閉路做人面識別就真<br />\n可以估計到監控已經去到好深入既地步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:58:17.000Z","msg":"香港冇 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7951583c14ad48552363e07a695a712c2c17f2a","tid":871390,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:00:33.000Z","msg":"可惜呢堆人名辯識系統&quot;姓黨&quot;"},{"pid":"c1b2bc2156d67b8de2c0efa172e527bd172fc42d","tid":871390,"uid":195588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dd4c4af3ebb72c6d640f33cfdf8649e78daabf7","tid":871390,"uid":113000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"安哂閉路做人面識別就真<br />\n可以估計到監控已經去到好深入既地步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"洗鬼估計咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" cla